The group of mercenaries Durable, led by Barney Ross, faces co-founder of the team, the Conrad Stoounmpanks. Ross was forced to kill Stoounmpanks, when he had turned into ruthless arms dealer, but after he survived, with the sole mission to destroy their supplies.
